  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to circulate your chakra throughout your entire network as pure fire and place a seal on your armor to contain the raging inferno. This fire begins to focus strongly on the body's natural chakra points and leaks out as rogue tongues of flame. For the duration of this jutsu:</p><ul><li><p>You gain immunity to Bludgeoning and Fire damage.</p></li><li><p>All Fire or Bludgeoning damage you deal treats immunity as resistance and ignores regular resistance.</p></li><li><p>Hostile creatures who come within 10 feet of the caster of this jutsu must make a Constitution Save, gaining 2 ranks of Burned on a fail and 1 rank on a success.</p></li><li><p>The effects of all Weapon and Armor Seals you are benefiting from are doubled.</p></li><li><p>You may not lose concentration on this jutsu as a result of damage</p></li></ul>",
